---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="About" description="The philosophy behind Archie.">

  <div class="about-outer">
    <div class="about-card">
      <div class="about-deco"></div>
      <article class="about-article">

        <section class="about-section">
          <h1 class="about-h1">Archie.</h1>
          <div class="about-body">
            <p>The name is a whisper from the woodlands, taken from <em>Myosotis sylvatica</em>.</p>
            <p>To the world, it is known simply as the <strong>Forget-Me-Not</strong>. A small, unassuming blue flower that carries a weight far heavier than its petals: a plea against oblivion.</p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <div class="about-divider"></div>

        <section class="about-section">
          <h2 class="about-h2">The Philosophy</h2>
          <div class="about-body">
            <p>In the Victorian language of flowers, the Forget-Me-Not symbolizes true love, faithfulness, and <em class="italic-mute">memories that never fade</em>.</p>
            <p>That is the sole purpose of this space.</p>
            <p>It is not a garden to be tended, but a <strong>Sanctuary</strong>. A place to keep the moments that matter, freezing them in digital amber so they are not washed away by time.</p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <div class="about-quote-wrap">
          <blockquote class="about-quote">
            "Silent as the blue flower,<br/>loud as the memory it holds."
          </blockquote>
        </div>

      </article>
    </div>
    <div class="enduring-label">ENDURING MEMORIES</div>
  </div>

</Base>

<style>
  .about-section { display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:1rem; }
  .about-outer { margin-top:2rem; }
  .about-card {
    background:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
    backdrop-filter:blur(22px); -webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(22px);
    border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
    padding:2.5rem 3.5rem; border-radius:1.75rem;
    position:relative; overflow:hidden;
    box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(100,149,237,0.08), 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
  }
  .about-deco {
    position:absolute; top:-40px; right:-40px;
    width:160px; height:160px;
    background:rgba(100,149,237,0.1);
    border-radius:50%; filter:blur(40px); pointer-events:none;
  }
  .about-article { position:relative; z-index:1; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:1.8rem; }

  .about-h1 {
    font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;
    font-size:clamp(3rem,10vw,4.5rem);
    font-weight:700; color:#6495ED;
    letter-spacing:-0.03em; margin-bottom:0.8rem;
  }
  .about-h2 {
    font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;
    font-size:1.8rem; font-weight:700;
    color:#334155; margin-bottom:1rem;
  }
  .about-body { display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:1rem; }
  .about-body p { color:#475569; font-size:1.1rem; line-height:1.9; font-weight:300; }
  .about-body em { font-style:italic; color:#1e293b; }
  .about-body strong { font-weight:700; color:#1e293b; }
  .italic-mute { font-style:italic; color:#64748b; }

  .about-divider { width:64px; height:1px; background:rgba(148,163,184,0.35); }

  .about-quote-wrap { padding-top:1rem; }
  .about-quote {
    font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;
    font-style:italic; font-size:1.3rem;
    color:#64748b; line-height:1.7; text-align:center;
  }

  .enduring-label {
    text-align:center; margin-top:2rem;
    font-size:0.6rem; color:#94a3b8;
    letter-spacing:0.25em; text-transform:uppercase; opacity:0.6;
    font-family:monospace;
  }

  @media (max-width:480px) {
    .about-card { padding:2rem 1.5rem; }
    .about-h1 { font-size:clamp(2.5rem,12vw,3.5rem); }
    .about-body p { font-size:1rem; }
    .about-quote { font-size:1.1rem; }
  }
</style>
